## ğŸ“Œ Overview
This project is an **AI-powered baby monitoring system** built with **YOLOv5**.  
It can **detect, track, and alert** when a baby moves outside a **predefined safety zone**.  
The system supports **real-time monitoring, local video processing, and YouTube video input**.

---

## ğŸš€ Features
- âœ… **Custom-trained YOLOv5 model** for baby detection  
- âœ… **Live tracking & zone-based alerts**  
- âœ… **YouTube video integration** for remote footage analysis  
- âœ… **Google Colab compatibility** for quick setup  
- âœ… **Sound alerts** when baby leaves the safe zone  

---

## ğŸ“Š Detection Box Colors
| Color | Meaning |
|-------|---------|
| ğŸŸ¦ Blue | Baby is **inside** the safety zone |
| ğŸŸ¥ Red  | Baby is **outside** the safety zone (**Alert!**) |

